data.description: ASSUMABLE VA LOAN WITH LOW INTEREST RATE. Nestled in the heart of picturesque Port Charlotte, in a quiet residential neighborhood, this exceptional home embodies the quintessential Florida dream. As you enter the property, you'll be enchanted by the lush landscaping that envelops this residence. It's more than just a house; it's your personal oasis. With a private backyard, screened in lanai and luxurious pool, home can be a vacation.    Step inside, and you'll find a meticulously updated kitchen adorned with wood cabinets, providing both elegance and functionality. The bathrooms have been thoughtfully updated and feature stylish vanities and stone countertops, creating a spa-like atmosphere. In fact, the stone countertops can be found not only in the bathrooms but also in the kitchen, offering a harmonious blend of aesthetics and durability.    Beyond the luxurious details, this home offers spaciousness at every turn. A walk-in closet ensures ample storage for your wardrobe, and the entire house exudes a feeling of airiness and comfort. With plenty of garage space, you'll have room for your vehicles and storage needs.    This property is the perfect blend of style, space, and serenity, making it an ideal place to call home in Port Charlotte. You won't be far anything including malls, shopping and schools. Experience the joy of living in your own private haven, surrounded by beautiful landscaping and featuring an amazing screened-in pool. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new Florida paradise; contact us today to schedule a viewing.
